2009年5月，兩隊在洋基體育場進行[[跨聯盟比賽|跨聯盟]]三連戰，當時費城人隊三戰兩勝<ref name="interleague">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091027&content_id=7561434&vkey=news_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi|title=Phillies-Yankees Interleague recap|first=Jenifer|last=Langosch|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-10-27|access-date=2011-03-01|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111152731/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091027&content_id=7561434&vkey=news_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi}}</ref>。雖然費城人隊[[終結者_(棒球)|終結者]][[布萊德·李吉|布萊德·李吉]]連續搞砸第二戰及第三戰的[[救援成功|救援機會]]，但他們最終戰還是在{{le|延長局數|extra innings|延長賽}}中逆轉勝<ref name="interleague"/>。

由於美聯贏下了當年的[[2009年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]，因此洋基隊取得本年世界大賽的[[主場優勢|主場優勢]]<ref name="allstar">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090715&content_id=5881270&vkey=allstar2009&fext=.jsp|title=AL retains World Series advantage|first=Anthony|last=Castrovince|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-07-15|access-date=2010-01-06| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100119084524/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20090715&content_id=5881270&vkey=allstar2009&fext=.jsp| archive-date=2010-01-19| dead-url= no}}</ref>。賽前，各大媒體都對本屆的東岸對戰組合報以熱烈的討論與分析，還大力吹捧兩隊的打線<ref name="verduccisi"/><ref name="packpunch">{{cite news |title=World Series packs punch at plate |author=Nightengale, Bob |newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=2009-10-27}}</ref><ref name="TSNpreview">{{cite web |url=https://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=296306 |title=2009 World Series Preview – Philadelphia vs. New York |date=2009-10-27 |publisher=The Sports Network |access-date=2010-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091108041238/http://www.tsn.ca/mlb/story/?id=296306 |archive-date=2009-11-08 |dead-url=yes  }}</ref><ref name="offense">{{cite news |title=The rest is hit story; Offence, offence and more offence mark these World Series contenders |last=Lott|first=John |newspaper=[[National_Post|National Post]] |date=2009-10-27}}</ref>，因為他們在各自的聯盟都是單場平均[[得分_(棒球)|得分]]最多的球隊<ref name="mlboffense">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2009.shtml|title=2009 Major League Baseball Team Statistics and Standings|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2010-01-20|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415210800/http://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/MLB/2009.shtml}}</ref>。其中洋基隊[[三壘手|三壘手]]A-ROD更是在2009年季後賽前幾輪打出佳績，與過往季後賽一條蟲的表現大相逕庭，博得不少媒體的特別關注<ref name="masslive">{{cite web |url=http://www.masslive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/10/post_127.html |title=Yankees slugger Alex Rodriguez deserves cheers for postseason performance |last=Chimelis |first=Ron |date=2009-10-21 |work=MassLive.com |publisher={{le|共和黨人報 (春田)|The Republican (Springfield)|共和黨人報}} |access-date=2010-01-20 |archive-date=2018-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725112957/https://www.masslive.com/sports/index.ssf/2009/10/post_127.html }}</ref><ref name="starledger">{{cite web |url=http://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2009/10/politi.html |title=As NY Yankees' Alex Rodriguez has postseason for the ages, it's best to appreciate, not ask why |last=Politi |first=Steve |date=2009-10-21 |work=NJ.com |publisher={{le|The Star-Ledger}} |access-date=2010-01-20 |archive-date=2018-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725110701/https://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2009/10/politi.html }}</ref><ref name="dayrod">{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091020&content_id=7508478 |title=Night-and-Day Rod: '09 Alex at his best |author=DiComo, Anthony |date=2009-10-21 |work=MLB.com |publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]] |access-date=2010-01-20 |archive-date=2013-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111152719/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091020&content_id=7508478 }}</ref>。兩隊打線一字排開就有20人曾入選[[美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]，另外還有三人曾贏得[[美國職棒大聯盟最有價值球員獎|年度最有價值球員獎]]<ref name="packpunch"/>，而且兩隊先發打線中，只有費城人隊[[捕手|捕手]]{{le|卡洛斯·魯伊斯 (棒球選手)|Carlos Ruiz (baseball)|卡洛斯·魯伊斯}}在2009年正規賽季的成績未達10發[[全壘打|全壘打]]<ref name="packpunch"/>。兩隊本季共轟出468發全壘打，比世界大賽史上任一對戰組合的全壘打總和都還多<ref name="packpunch"/>。

兩隊投手群也是賽前被熱烈討論的主要議題之一<ref name="TSNpreview"/>。像是第一戰的先發投手（C·C·沙巴西亞和克里夫·李）都被視為王牌投手<ref name="offense"/>，兩人賽前在2009年季後賽合計[[防禦率|防禦率]]來到極具宰制力的0.96<ref name="clunkers">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/27/sports/baseball/27kepner.html |title=Baseball Hopes to Break a Streak of Clunker Series |last=Kepner |first=Tyler |date=2009-10-26 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |access-date=2010-01-21 |archive-date=2021-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421081006/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/27/sports/baseball/27kepner.html }}</ref>。這個對決還有個看點，就是沙巴西亞和李曾互為[[克里夫蘭印地安人隊|克里夫蘭印地安人隊]]隊友，也都曾各自在印地安人隊拿下[[賽揚獎|賽揚獎]]<ref name="clunkers"/><ref name="joepos">{{cite news |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2009/writers/joe_posnanski/10/28/lee.sabathia/index.html |title=World Series lament for Indians fans: What might have been |last=Posnanski|first=Joe |date=2009-10-28|work=SI.com |publisher=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]] |access-date=2010-01-21| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100104110958/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2009/writers/joe_posnanski/10/28/lee.sabathia/index.html| archive-date=2010-01-04| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/columnist/lopresti/2009-10-29-former-indians-pitchers-lopo_N.htm |title=Spurned Cleveland watches former Indians with a sigh |author=Lopresti, Mike |date=2009-10-29 |newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |access-date=2010-01-21 |archive-date=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604005434/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/columnist/lopresti/2009-10-29-former-indians-pitchers-lopo_N.htm }}</ref>。在季後賽投手布陣方面，洋基隊[[總教練_(棒球)|總教練]][[喬·吉拉迪|喬·吉拉迪]]採用的是三人輪轉的{{le|先發輪值|starting rotation}}，而費城人則是以四人輪轉應戰<ref name="3man">{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/news/story?id=4611766 |title=Girardi may go with three-man rotation |date=2009-10-29 |author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]] |publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures |access-date=2010-01-21 |archive-date=2014-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829074853/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/news/story?id=4611766 }}</ref><ref name="usatight">{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/playoffs/2009-10-27-world-series-breakdown_N.htm |title=Yankees and Phillies on track for a tight Series |date=2009-10-28 |author=Ortiz, Jorge |author2=Shandler, Ron |newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |access-date=2010-01-21 |archive-date=2012-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501092548/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/playoffs/2009-10-27-world-series-breakdown_N.htm }}</ref>。兩隊輪值間的差異讓[[今日美國|今日美國]]認為費城人隊將在世界大賽中「佔據優勢（edge）」，因為世界大賽的舉行期間較前幾輪的季後賽為少，使得採用三人輪轉的先發輪值將較為不利<ref name="usatight"/>。[[ESPN|ESPN]]體育記者{{le|傑納·沃傑霍夫斯基|Gene Wojciechowski}}批評吉拉迪的戰略，認為第五戰或第六戰應由[[查德·高汀|查德·高汀]]上陣先發，而非推出僅休息三天的A·J·柏奈特或是[[安迪·派提特|安迪·派提特]]<ref name="woj3man">{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/columns/story?columnist=wojciechowski_gene&id=4612984&sportCat=mlb|title=Girardi needs to give it a rest|date=2009-10-31|first=Gene|last=Wojciechowski|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|access-date=2010-03-25|archive-date=2016-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107115308/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/columns/story?columnist=wojciechowski_gene&id=4612984&sportCat=mlb}}</ref>。沃傑霍夫斯基還說到，即便沙巴西亞已證明自己可以在縮短休息天數下仍能上陣，還是應當讓柏奈特和派提特回到正規賽季時的輪值方式<ref name="woj3man"/>。世界大賽開打前，柏奈特差勁的先發表現讓他備受批評<ref name="clunkers"/>，特別是他在[[2009年美國聯盟冠軍賽|美聯冠軍賽]]第五戰主投六局就失了六分<ref name="ALCSg5">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ANA/ANA200910220.shtml|title=October 22, 2009 American League Championship Series (ALCS) Game 5, Yankees at Angels|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2010-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116155343/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ANA/ANA200910220.shtml}}</ref>。然而柏奈特先前也曾在短暫休息後先發拿下佳績，此戰前四次這類先發均拿下勝投，留下防禦率2.33的紀錄。[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]的泰勒·凱普納（Tyler Kepner）則認為吉拉迪之所以擺出三人輪轉的佈陣，是因為對於四號先發的部分，他沒有太多選擇，無論是高汀或是[[喬巴·張伯倫|喬巴·張伯倫]]，他們在正規賽季都沒有常駐於先發輪值中，而且季後賽前幾輪都拉往牛棚支援<ref name="woj3man"/><ref name="batsblog">{{cite news|url=http://bats.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/10/27/yankees-may-use-a-three-man-rotation/|title=Yankees May Use a Three-Man Rotation | last=Kepner | first=Tyler |date=2009-10-27|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2010-03-26| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100327234601/http://bats.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/10/27/yankees-may-use-a-three-man-rotation/| archive-date= 2010-03-27 | dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/14/sports/baseball/14yankees.html|title=Barring Rain, Yanks Consider 3-Man Rotation|last=Kepner|first=Tyler|date=2009-10-13|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2010-03-26|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075506/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/14/sports/baseball/14yankees.html}}</ref>。

兩隊的終結者馬里安諾·李維拉和布萊德·李吉也同樣受到矚目，因為他們是2009年季後賽裡唯二沒有搞砸救援機會的終結者，而其他季後賽隊伍的終結者們，在世界大賽前所舉行的24場季後賽中，便救援失敗了11次<ref name="closerpreview">{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091027&content_id=7558018&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Closer matchup reflects playoff perfection |author=Langosch, Jenifer |date=2009-10-27 |work=MLB.com |publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]] |access-date=2010-03-17 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104134147/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091027&content_id=7558018&vkey=ps2009news&c_id=mlb&fext=.jsp }}</ref>。兩人在季後賽表現出色，但李吉當年正規賽季防禦率高達7.21，而李維拉的成績則是1.76<ref name="closerpreview"/><ref name="mobref">{{cite web| url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/riverma01.shtml|title=Mariano Rivera Statistics and History|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2010-03-17| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100208150022/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/riverma01.shtml| archive-date=2010-02-08| dead-url= no}}</ref>。此外，李吉2009年的成績與去年的紀錄<ref group="註">2008年李吉拿下全部的41次救援機會，且出賽62場的防禦率僅1.95，還奪下92次三振</ref>相去甚遠，因此今日美國認為洋基隊在這方面占優，還特別提出李吉於同年稍早兩隊交戰的正規賽中，曾兩度登板救援失敗<ref name="usatight"/>。

