==背景==
本屆世界大賽於2009年10月28日開打，係史上最晚開賽的世界大賽，比先前最遲的{{wsy|2001}}還要晚了一天<ref>{{cite news |first=Bob|last=Dutton|title=World Series Buzz: Martinez ruminates on New York|work={{le|The Kansas City Star}}|date=2009-10-29}}</ref>。第四戰舉行於11月1日星期日，而決勝的第六戰則於11月4日開打。本屆是史上第三次結束於十月以外月份的世界大賽；第一次是{{wsy|1918}}，當年賽季因[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]而縮水，所以整個系列賽都在九月舉行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/postseason/mlb_ws_recaps.jsp?feature=1918|title=World Series History|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|access-date=2010-01-06|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115055353/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/history/postseason/mlb_ws_recaps.jsp?feature=1918}}</ref>；另外一次是{{wsy|2001}}，該季正規賽因[[九一一襲擊事件|九一一襲擊事件]]而延賽，導致最終世界大賽需打至11月才能完賽<ref>{{cite video|title=Nine Innings from Ground Zero|people=Shapiro, Ouisie (writer)|medium=DVD}}</ref>。

本季開打不久後，[[美國職業棒球大聯盟主席|大聯盟主席]]{{le|巴德·賽里格|Bud Selig}}就表達出將世界大賽改為白天舉行的興趣<ref>{{cite news|title=World Series could get earlier starting times|url=http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/30111531/|work=[[NBC_Sports|NBC Sports]]|agency={{le|體育新聞|Sporting News}}|date=2009-04-08|access-date=2011-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115021237/http://nbcsports.msnbc.com/id/30111531|archive-date=2010-01-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。而本屆世界大賽也確實是自30年以來，首度將開賽時間提前至[[北美東部時區|美國東部時間]]晚間八點前，但仍舊未施行日間比賽制度<ref>{{cite web |title= WS games to start 40 minutes earlier|url= http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4174213|author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|date=2009-05-18|access-date=2009-05-18| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090520134209/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4174213| archive-date=2009-05-20| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Larry|last=Fine|title=Selig mulls World Series changes, not to home comforts|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/03/us-baseball-selig-idUSTRE4B18VG20081203|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2008-12-02|access-date=2008-12-03|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103200418/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/03/us-baseball-selig-idUSTRE4B18VG20081203}}</ref>。第四戰當天下午，[[費城老鷹隊|費城老鷹隊]]與[[紐約巨人隊|紐約巨人隊]]交手的[[國家美式足球聯盟|美式足球]]比賽因舉行地{{le|林肯金融體育場|Lincoln Financial Field}}就在[[市民銀行球場|市民銀行球場]]街口對面，故其為避免這場比賽結束時影響到世界大賽第四戰的開打，將開賽時間提前到下午一點<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsday.com/blogs/sports/watchdog-1.812020/giants-jets-play-at-same-time-11-1-1.1520052|title=Giants, Jets play at same time 11/1|first=Neil|last=Best|work={{le|Newsday}}|date=2009-10-13|access-date=2009-10-13| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091015110950/http://www.newsday.com/blogs/sports/watchdog-1.812020/giants-jets-play-at-same-time-11-1-1.1520052| archive-date=2009-10-15| dead-url= no}}</ref>。在市民銀行球場舉行的第五戰同樣強碰[[國家冰球聯盟|國家冰球聯盟]]的比賽，那天[[費城飛人隊|費城飛人隊]]要在[[富國銀行中心|美聯銀行中心]]迎戰[[坦帕灣閃電隊|坦帕灣閃電隊]]，為避免衝突，冰球比賽的開賽時間也從晚上七點提前到下午五點<ref>{{cite web|url=http://flyers.nhl.com/club/news.htm?id=502389|title=Flyers Change Start Time of November 2nd Game|date=2009-10-16|access-date=2009-10-29|publisher=philadelphiaflyers.com| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091021142810/http://flyers.nhl.com/club/news.htm?id=502389| archive-date=2009-10-21| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

本次世界大賽的[[裁判_(棒壘球)|裁判]]是{{le|蓋里·戴維斯 (裁判)|Gerry Davis (umpire)|蓋里·戴維斯}}（主審）、{{le|傑夫·尼爾森 (裁判)|Jeff Nelson (umpire)|傑夫·尼爾森}}、{{le|布萊恩·戈爾曼|Brian Gorman}}、{{le|麥克·艾弗特 (棒球)|Mike Everitt (baseball)|麥克·艾弗特}}、{{le|達納·德穆斯|Dana DeMuth}}、{{le|喬·韋斯特 (裁判)|Joe West (umpire)|喬·韋斯特}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Meet the World Series umpiring crew|url= http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/news/story?id=4600610|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|date=2009-10-27|access-date=2009-11-17| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091031194903/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/news/story?id=4600610| archive-date=2009-10-31| dead-url= no}}</ref>。本次世界大賽的全體工作人員中，至少有一名裁判未曾出現過去25次世界大賽中的24次；然而即使前幾輪季後賽中有不少裁判誤判，但這名裁判卻未曾發生<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091022&content_id=7527964&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=MLB may use veteran umps in Fall Classic: Change would break longstanding baseball tradition |first=Adam |last=McCalvy |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]] |date=2009-10-22 |access-date=2011-02-24 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104130502/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091022&content_id=7527964&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb&fext=.jsp }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091022&content_id=7524222&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Umpire's call on Damon draws attention: Yankee looked safe at first base on third-inning groundout |first=Anthony |last=Castrovince |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]] |date=2009-10-23 |access-date=2011-02-24 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104130345/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091022&content_id=7524222&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb&fext=.jsp }}</ref><ref name="wojreplay">{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/columns/story?columnist=wojciechowski_gene&id=4598071&sportCat=mlb |title=Instant replay for the World Series? Yes|first=Gene|last=Wojciechowski|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures |date=2009-10-27|access-date=2009-11-17| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091030130026/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/columns/story?columnist=wojciechowski_gene&id=4598071&sportCat=mlb| archive-date=2009-10-30| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

費城人隊[[2008年世界大賽|前一年的世界大賽]]擊敗了{{le|2008年坦帕灣光芒隊球季|2008 Tampa Bay Rays season|坦帕灣光芒隊}}，奪得了隊史第二座世界大賽冠軍。洋基隊前次打入世界大賽是{{wsy|2003}}，但當年敗於{{le|2003年佛羅里達馬林魚隊球季|2003 Florida Marlins season|佛羅里達馬林魚隊}}，而上次贏得世界大賽冠軍已是{{wsy|2000}}擊敗{{le|2000年紐約大都會隊球季|2000 New York Mets season|紐約大都會隊}}的那次。這是洋基隊與費城人隊史上第五次在世界大賽交手，也是自{{wsy|1950}}以來首度交鋒<ref name="1950WS">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1950_WS.shtml|title=1950 World Series – NYY vs. PHI|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2009-12-28|archive-date=2008-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622220954/http://www.baseball-reference.com/postseason/1950_WS.shtml}}</ref>。此外費城人隊已經連續四次在世界大賽與美聯東區的隊伍對戰，而洋基隊也是在最近五次世界大賽中第四度迎戰國聯東區的對手<ref name="wshistory"/>。

本屆世界大賽有兩個暱稱：「收費高速公路大戰（Turnpike Series）」，意指連接紐約及費城的[[紐澤西收費高速公路|紐澤西收費高速公路]]<ref name="verduccisi">{{cite news |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2009/writers/tom_verducci/10/27/five.cuts/index.html |title=How can the Phillies beat the Yankees in the 2009 World Series? |first=Tom|last=Verducci|date=2009-10-28|work=SI.com |publisher=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]] |access-date=2010-01-21| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100205111403/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2009/writers/tom_verducci/10/27/five.cuts/index.html| archive-date=2010-02-05| dead-url= no}}</ref>；以及「自由大戰（Liberty Series）」，指的是兩市的象徵：費城的[[自由鐘|自由鐘]]及紐約的[[自由女神像|自由女神像]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=DAN PARZYCH |date=2009-10-28 |title=Phillies vs. Yankees Causing Fans to Become "Frienemies" in World Series |url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/279950-phillies-yankees-causing-fans-to-become-frienemies-in-world-series |website=Bleacher Report |accessdate=2021-03-23 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423120125/https://bleacherreport.com/articles/279950-phillies-yankees-causing-fans-to-become-frienemies-in-world-series }}</ref>。

截至{{mlby|2020}}，這是洋基隊的最後一座世界大賽冠軍，也是兩隊最後一次打入世界大賽的一年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091026&content_id=7549598&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title= Liberty Series: Statue, Bell Set for Clash |access-date=2009-10-26|last=Newman|first=Mark|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-10-26| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091027192133/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091026&content_id=7549598&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-10-27| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

