賽前[[Jay-Z|Jay-Z]]和[[艾莉西亞·凱斯|艾莉西亞·凱斯]]為洋基體育場的球迷們共同獻唱「[[帝國之心|帝國之心]]」<ref name="jayzkeys">{{cite web| url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1625161/20091029/keys_alicia.jhtml|title=Jay-Z And Alicia Keys Pump Up World Series Crowd In NYC|first=Jayson|last=Rodriguez|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|access-date=2009-11-02|date=2009-10-29| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091102065545/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1625161/20091029/keys_alicia.jhtml| archive-date=2009-11-02| dead-url= no}}</ref>。[[佩卓·馬丁尼茲|佩卓·馬丁尼茲]]這場先發是自[[2004年美國聯盟冠軍賽|2004年美國聯盟冠軍賽]]以來<ref group="註">當年他還在{{le|2004年波士頓紅襪隊球季|2004 Boston Red Sox season|紅襪隊}}時也參與了這場[[基襪世仇|基襪世仇]]的比賽</ref>，首度在季後賽與洋基隊碰頭，同時也是他生涯第二度在世界大賽先發<ref name="pedrobref">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/martipe02.shtml|title=Pedro Martínez Statistics and History|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2009-10-30|archive-date=2010-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100104120539/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/m/martipe02.shtml}}</ref>。馬丁尼茲在第二戰「重返洋基體育場」引起了眾多媒體關注，正如賽前新聞發布會上他對記者所言：「當有60,000人在呼喊你名字，等待你的投球時，你就必須將自己視為一個特別的人，一個真正有目的的人<ref group="註">When you have 60,000 people chanting your name, waiting for you to throw the ball, you have to consider yourself someone special, someone that really has a purpose out there.</ref>。」 <ref>{{cite web|last=Silverman|first=Mike|url=http://news.bostonherald.com/sports/baseball/other_mlb/view.bg?articleid=1208123&srvc=sports&position=0|title='Influential' Pedro Martinez holds court|work=Boston Herald|date=2009-10-29|access-date=2010-07-22|archive-date=2012-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402214015/http://news.bostonherald.com/sports/baseball/other_mlb/view.bg?articleid=1208123&srvc=sports&position=0}}</ref>

第二戰開打後，費城人隊二局上半面對[[A·J·柏奈特|A·J·柏奈特]]先馳得點，先靠著[[勞爾·伊巴涅斯|勞爾·伊巴涅斯]][[場地二壘安打|場地二壘安打]]上壘，再靠{{le|麥特·史泰爾斯|Matt Stairs}}的一壘安打回來得分，取得1比0領先<ref name="game2bref">{{cite web| url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA200910290.shtml|title=October 29, 2009 World Series Game 2, Phillies at Yankees|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2009-10-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091102110038/http://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA200910290.shtml| archive-date=2009-11-02| dead-url= no}}</ref>。但洋基隊靠著[[馬克·特薛拉|馬克·特薛拉]]及[[松井秀喜|松井秀喜]]分別在四局下半及六局下半的各一發陽春砲，超前比數<ref name="game2bref"/>。七局下半，馬丁尼茲一上來接連被[[傑瑞·小赫爾斯頓|傑瑞·小赫爾斯頓]]及[[梅基·卡布瑞拉|梅基·卡布瑞拉]]擊出安打被迫下場，而接替投球的[[朴贊浩|朴贊浩]]又被[[荷黑·波沙達|荷黑·波沙達]]擊出一分打點的一壘安打<ref>{{cite web |first=Bryan|last=Hoch|title=Yanks take Classic duel to pull even|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091029&content_id=7572446&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-10-30|access-date=2009-10-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091102045339/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091029&content_id=7572446&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-11-02| dead-url= no}}</ref>。接著[[強尼·戴蒙|強尼·戴蒙]]在一二壘有人<ref group="註">波沙達在一壘，卡布瑞拉在二壘</ref>的情形下，打出一壘方向較低的平飛球。費城人隊一壘手[[萊恩·霍華德|萊恩·霍華德]]抓到了這顆球，並傳給二壘手觸殺已跑到二壘的波沙達。由於一壘審{{le|布萊恩·戈爾曼|Brian Gorman}}判定霍華德在空中接到球，因此這球變成結束該半局的雙殺守備。但波沙達和總教練[[喬·吉拉迪|喬·吉拉迪]]都上前強烈抗議，認為這球在被接到前就已落地，但最終未獲裁判採納及改判。ESPN也將其報導為戈爾曼的誤判<ref>{{cite web |title=Game 2 calls draw more scrutiny|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/news/story?id=4607883|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|date=2009-10-30|access-date=2009-12-08| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091102180815/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/news/story?id=4607883| archive-date=2009-11-02| dead-url= no}}</ref>。這次誤判也是戈爾曼在第二戰兩個被嚴厲批評的判決之一<ref>{{cite news |title=Time for video replay in baseball before something really sorry happens... again |url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2010169691_time_for_video_replay_in_baseb.html|date=2009-10-30|newspaper=[[西雅圖時報|西雅圖時報]]|first=Geoff|last=Baker|access-date=2009-12-08| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091104083300/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2010169691_time_for_video_replay_in_baseb.html| archive-date=2009-11-04| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=The time has come for MLB to implement instant replay |url=http://www.nesn.com/2009/10/the-time-has-come-for-mlb-to-implement-instant-replay.html|date=2009-10-31|publisher={{le|新英格蘭體育網|New England Sports Network}}|first=David|last=Heck|access-date=2009-12-08| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091205005355/http://www.nesn.com/2009/10/the-time-has-come-for-mlb-to-implement-instant-replay.html| archive-date=2009-12-05| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="closecallsgame2">{{cite news|first=David|last=Waldstein|title=In World Series, Umpires Find Themselves Back in Center of Dispute|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/30/sports/baseball/30umps.html?_r=1|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2009-10-30|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075500/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/30/sports/baseball/30umps.html?_r=1}}</ref>。

洋基隊先發投手柏奈特主投七局僅失一分，第八局由[[馬里安諾·李維拉|馬里安諾·李維拉]]接替登板<ref name="game2bref"/>。八局上半一出局後，費城人隊靠著[[吉米·羅林斯|吉米·羅林斯]]的保送及[[謝恩·維克托里諾|謝恩·維克托里諾]]的一壘安打攻占兩個壘包<ref name="game2bref"/>，接著[[蔡斯·阿特利|蔡斯·阿特利]]打出滾地球，雖然幾乎要安全上壘，但最終還是形成結束半局的雙殺打<ref name="game2bref"/>。這個判決是戈爾曼在第二戰的第二次爭議判決，他本人事後也承認這是個誤判，並說道：「從定格畫面來看，當（阿特利）踩到壘包時，回傳球似乎還離（特薛拉）有一小段距離<ref group="註">"on a freeze frame, it looks like there's a little bit of a ball outside [Teixeira's] glove when [Utley] hits the bag."</ref>」<ref name="closecallsgame2"/>。最終柏奈特在第二站拿下勝投<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2009/10/ny_yankees_beat_philadelphia_p.html|title=NY Yankees beat Philadelphia Phillies, 3-1, in Game 2 of World Series|work=NJ.com|last=Carig|first=Marc|date=2009-10-29|access-date=2018-10-28|archive-date=2018-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028152525/https://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2009/10/ny_yankees_beat_philadelphia_p.html}}</ref>，李維拉也在上場救援39球並成功製造六個出局數後，奪下生涯季後賽的第38次救援成功，以及世界大賽中的第十次<ref>{{cite news |first=Erik|last=Boland|title=Rivera gets six-out save as Yankees win Game 2, 3–1|url=http://www.newsday.com/sports/baseball/yankees/rivera-gets-six-out-save-as-yankees-win-game-2-3-1-1.1557551|newspaper={{le|Newsday}}|date=2009-10-30|access-date=2009-10-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091102093726/http://www.newsday.com/sports/baseball/yankees/rivera-gets-six-out-save-as-yankees-win-game-2-3-1-1.1557551| archive-date=2009-11-02| dead-url= yes}}</ref>。

