這場比賽因雨延遲了80分鐘，最後於晚間9點17分開打<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2009/11/01/us-baseball-series-rain-idUSTRE5A000I20091101|title=World Series gets underway after rain delay|date=2009-10-31|access-date=2012-12-20|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103200148/http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/11/01/us-baseball-series-rain-idUSTRE5A000I20091101}}</ref>。在開賽儀式上，電視劇「[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]」的演員陣容在{{le|安珀·萊利|Amber Riley}}的領唱下演唱[[國歌|國歌]]，同時豎立巨幅美國國旗並有數名軍方成員列席<ref name="glee">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091031&content_id=7586030&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=MLB Stands Up to Cancer in Game 3|access-date=2010-03-16|last=Newman|first=Mark|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103111319/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091031&content_id=7586030&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb}}</ref><ref name="flaggame3">{{cite web|url=http://www.512aw.afrc.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123176480|title=Reservist takes part in opening ceremony of Game 3 of World Series|access-date=2010-03-16|last=Losurdo|first=Marnee|work={{le|512th Airlift Wing}}|publisher=[[United_States_Air_Force|United States Air Force]]|date=2009-11-06|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722180557/http://www.512aw.afrc.af.mil/news/story.asp?id=123176480|archive-date=2011-07-22}}</ref>。此戰同樣由費城人隊先馳得點：二局下半，[[傑森·沃斯|傑森·沃斯]]一上來就轟出全壘打，接著費城人隊又靠著滿壘時的保送以及[[高飛犧牲打|高飛犧牲打]]取得3比0領先<ref name="game3bref">{{cite web| url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/PHI/PHI200910310.shtml|title=October 31, 2009 World Series Game 3, Yankees at Phillies|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2009-11-02| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091108163317/http://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/PHI/PHI200910310.shtml| archive-date=2009-11-08| dead-url= no}}</ref>。洋基隊在四局上半吹起反攻號角，馬克·特薛拉獲保送後，[[艾力士·羅德里奎茲|艾力士·羅德里奎茲]]打右外野深遠飛球命中全壘打牆上彈出，原本這球被判為場地二壘安打，特薛拉推進至三壘，但裁判經過{{le|美國職棒大聯盟即時重播|Instant replay in Major League Baseball|即時重播}}後，發現該球打中一台攝影機且該攝影機位於全壘打牆上方，從而改判為兩分打點全壘打<ref name="cameramove">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7594160&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Camera moved after A-Rod homer|access-date=2009-11-01|last=DiComo|first=Anthony|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091104234934/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7594160&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-11-04| dead-url= no}}</ref>，同時這也是A-ROD在世界大賽中的首安<ref name="arodbref">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/rodrial01.shtml|title=Alex Rodriguez Statistics and History|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2009-11-02|archive-date=2010-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100712225632/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/rodrial01.shtml}}</ref>。本支全壘打也是首支在季後賽因即時重播而改判的全壘打<ref name="cameramove"/>。另外，這顆球擊中的是[[福斯廣播公司|福斯廣播公司]]及大聯盟所共有的攝影機，這支攝影機當時剛好略為深入右外野全壘打牆內<ref name="cameramove"/>。後來這支攝影機在第四戰回歸，其鏡頭這次就與全壘打牆對齊了<ref name="cameramove"/>。巧合的是在本季正規賽時，A-ROD也有一支全壘打是因重播而改判的<ref name="arod08replay">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080903&content_id=3412816&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title= Instant replay used for first time|access-date=2009-11-01|last=Chastain|first=Bill|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2008-09-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091103075313/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080903&content_id=3412816&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-11-03| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

五局上半，[[尼可拉斯·史威瑟|尼可拉斯·史威瑟]]開局的二壘安打又開啟洋基隊的攻勢，隨後[[安迪·派提特|安迪·派提特]]打出中外野方向的一壘安打送回史威瑟追平比數<ref name="game3bref"/>。這分是派提特生涯季後賽首分打點，也是洋基隊自{{wsy|1964}}的{{le|吉姆·包頓|Jim Bouton}}以來，首位在世界大賽打出打點的投手<ref name="bouton">{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=stark_jayson&id=4613099|title=2009 World Series: New York Yankees' Pettitte knows his way around this stage |access-date=2009-11-02|date=2009-10-31|first=Jayson|last=Stark|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091104235650/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=stark_jayson&id=4613099| archive-date=2009-11-04| dead-url= no}}</ref>。下一棒[[德瑞克·基特|德瑞克·基特]]又補上一支一壘安打，接著強尼·戴蒙的二壘安打一棒送回派提特和基特，幫助洋基隊取得5比3領先<ref name="game3bref"/>。[[科爾·漢梅爾斯|科爾·漢梅爾斯]]保送了特薛拉後下場，由[[J·A·哈普|J·A·哈普]]登板投球。哈普成功在五局上關門未失分，但下一局還是被尼可拉斯·史威瑟的陽春全壘打砲轟，兩隊比數擴大到三分差<ref name="game3bref"/>。六局下半，沃斯首棒上來又擊出全壘打，將比數追近為4比6<ref name="game3bref"/>，他也成為費城人隊第二位於本屆世界大賽擊出多發全壘打的球員。

七局上半，{{le|查德·杜賓|Chad Durbin}}接替哈普投球，但他先保送了強尼·戴蒙，隨後又被後者[[盜壘|盜上]]二壘。接著A-ROD遭[[觸身球|觸身球]]保送，洋基隊再靠[[荷黑·波沙達|荷黑·波沙達]]的一壘安打送回戴蒙，再下一城<ref name="game3bref"/>。洋基隊在七局下半換上[[喬巴·張伯倫|喬巴·張伯倫]]登板接替佩提特，並成功連拿三個出局數<ref name="game3bref"/>。八局上半，費城人隊的{{le|布雷特·邁爾斯|Brett Myers}}解決頭兩名打者後，遭到[[代打|代打]]張伯倫的[[松井秀喜|松井秀喜]]狙擊，洋基隊取得8比4領先<ref name="pinchhithr">{{cite web|url=http://www.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7591284&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Lack of DH doesn't hinder Yankees|access-date=2009-11-01|last=Ghiroli|first=Brittnay|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100221120621/http://mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7591284&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|archive-date=2010-02-21}}</ref>。九局下半，[[菲爾·休斯|菲爾·休斯]]僅投1/3局就因被{{le|卡洛斯·魯伊斯 (棒球選手)|Carlos Ruiz (baseball)|卡洛斯·魯伊斯}}砲轟陽春全壘打下場，改由[[馬里安諾·李維拉|馬里安諾·李維拉]]救援<ref name="game3bref"/>。李維拉最終只以五球就奪兩出局，結束比賽<ref name="game3bref"/>。本場比賽是佩提特生涯第17場季後賽勝投，刷新他在大聯盟締造的紀錄<ref name="bouton"/>。

