本場比賽開打前，[[德瑞克·基特|德瑞克·基特]]和[[亞伯特·普荷斯|亞伯特·普荷斯]]獲選為2009年[[漢克·阿倫獎|漢克·阿倫獎]]得主<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7595224&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Pujols, Jeter winners of Aaron Award |access-date=2009-11-04|last=Bloom|first=Barry|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091104234955/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7595224&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-11-04| dead-url= no}}</ref>。這場比賽是洋基隊總教練[[喬·吉拉迪|喬·吉拉迪]]採用三人輪轉的{{le|先發輪值|starting rotation}}後的首場考驗，因為[[C·C·沙巴西亞|C·C·沙巴西亞]]僅休了三天就再度上陣，這比他在正規賽時的休賽輪值還短<ref>{{cite web|url=http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=291031122&teams=new-york-yankees-vs-philadelphia-phillies|author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|title=A-Rod starts rally, Pettitte hits RBI single as Yankees claim 2–1 lead over Phillies|date=2009-10-31|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|access-date=2010-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303185556/http://scores.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=291031122&teams=new-york-yankees-vs-philadelphia-phillies}}</ref>。一局上半，基特一上來就擊出一壘安打上壘，隨後[[強尼·戴蒙|強尼·戴蒙]]的二壘安打助隊攻佔二、三壘<ref name="game4bref">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/PHI/PHI200911010.shtml|title=November 1, 2009 World Series Game 4, Yankees at Phillies|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|work=[[Baseball-Reference|Baseball-Reference]]|access-date=2009-01-12|archive-date=2009-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091105063817/http://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/PHI/PHI200911010.shtml}}</ref>。接著[[馬克·特薛拉|馬克·特薛拉]]的滾地球雖然出局，但成功送回基特得分<ref name="game4bref"/>。下一棒[[艾力士·羅德里奎茲|A-ROD]]遭到[[觸身球|觸身球]]保送<ref name="game4bref"/>，由於賽前他已遭觸身球兩次，因此裁判給予雙方板凳各一次警告<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7594158&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Benches warned after A-Rod plunking|access-date=2009-11-02|last=DiComo|first=Anthony|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091104234929/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7594158&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-11-04| dead-url= no}}</ref>。[[荷黑·波沙達|荷黑·波沙達]]又接著擊出[[高飛犧牲打|高飛犧牲打]]再下一城，洋基隊取得2比0領先<ref name="game4bref"/>。費城人隊很快就在一局下半發動反攻，藉由[[謝恩·維克托里諾|謝恩·維克托里諾]]和[[蔡斯·阿特利|蔡斯·阿特利]]的兩支二壘安打扳回一城<ref name="game4bref"/>。沙巴西亞{{le|故意四壞保送|Intentional base on balls}}了[[傑森·沃斯|傑森·沃斯]]，但最終未再於該局失分<ref name="game4bref"/>。四局下半，費城人隊先靠[[萊恩·霍華德|萊恩·霍華德]]的一壘安打上壘，隨後又盜上二壘，並靠著{{le|佩卓·菲利茲|Pedro Feliz}}的一壘安打回來扳平比數<ref name="game4bref"/>。但這分卻出現爭議，因為透過[[即時重播|即時重播]]可以發現到霍華德滑回本壘時，其實並未碰到[[本壘板|本壘板]]：當沙巴西亞傳向二壘時，裁判{{le|麥克·艾弗特 (棒球)|Mike Everitt (baseball)|麥克·艾弗特}}示意霍華德因守方嘗試觸殺菲利茲而安全上壘。沙巴西亞接著對下一棒{{le|卡洛斯·魯伊斯 (棒球選手)|Carlos Ruiz (baseball)|卡洛斯·魯伊斯}}故意四壞球保送，從而失去申訴霍華德本壘爭議的權利<ref name="FOX4">{{cite video|title=Major League Baseball on Fox: Game 4 of the 2009 World Series|medium=television|publisher=Fox|date=2009-11-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7597644&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Howard scores without touching plate|access-date=2009-11-02|last=Langosch|first=Jennifer|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100221120217/http://mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7597644&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|archive-date=2010-02-21}}</ref>。

五局上半，首名打者[[尼可拉斯·史威瑟|尼可拉斯·史威瑟]]獲保送後，靠著下一棒[[梅基·卡布瑞拉|梅基·卡布瑞拉]]的一壘安打攻占二壘<ref name="game4bref"/>。之後史威瑟靠著基特一壘安打跑回領先分，戴蒙隨後補上一壘安打送回卡布瑞拉，再下一城<ref name="game4bref"/>。六局下半，卡布雷拉因腿後肌受傷退場，由[[布萊特·加德納|布萊特·加德納]]{{le|換防 (棒球)|defensive substitution|接管}}中外野防區<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=291101122|title=New York Yankees vs. Philadelphia Phillies – Recap – November 10, 2009 – ESPN |access-date=2009-11-02|author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091105033102/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/recap?gameId=291101122| archive-date=2009-11-05| dead-url= no}}</ref>。費城人隊於七局上半換上[[朴贊浩|朴贊浩]]接替先發的{{le|喬·布蘭頓|Joe Blanton}}投球，並成功守下該局未失分<ref name="game4bref"/>。七局下半兩出局後，[[蔡斯·阿特利|蔡斯·阿特利]]轟出個人本次世界大賽的第三發全壘打，將比數追成3比4。洋基隊換投[[達馬索·馬提|達馬索·馬提]]，並成功抓到該局最後一個出局數止血<ref name="game4bref"/>。

[[萊恩·麥德森|萊恩·麥德森]]於八局上登板，即便他送出一次保送還被敲一支一壘安打，卻還是讓洋基隊無功而返<ref name="game4bref"/>。喬巴·張伯倫在八局下半接替馬提投球，雖先三振掉頭兩名打者，卻還是在結束該局前被菲利茲打出追平轟<ref name="game4bref"/>。

九局上半，費城人隊派出守護神[[布萊德·李吉|布萊德·李吉]]，先後讓松井秀喜和基特分別以飛球和三振出局，但在與戴蒙纏鬥九球後<ref group="註">曾一度取得兩好球，而且還包括四次界外球</ref>，還是被後者擊出一壘安打<ref name="game4bref"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=stark_jayson&id=4615712|title=Damon steals the show|author=Stark, Jayson|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|date=November 2009|access-date=2021-04-21|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423120132/https://www.espn.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=stark_jayson&id=4615712}}</ref>。接著輪到特薛拉打擊時，戴蒙先成功盜上二壘，再靠對手針對特薛拉的{{le|棒球守位|Baseball positions|守備布陣}}盜上毫無防備的三壘<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7594166&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Johnny lately: Yanks' 9th makes it a 3–1 Series |access-date=2009-11-02|last=Hoch|first=Brian|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091104234938/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091101&content_id=7594166&vkey=recap&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2009-11-04| dead-url= no}}</ref>。許多新聞出處都將其稱為「狂奔（mad dash）」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=crasnick_jerry&id=4615700|first=Jerry|last=Crasnick|title=Phillies awoke nearly silent Rodriguez|date=2009-11-01|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|access-date=2010-03-29|archive-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211234002/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=crasnick_jerry&id=4615700}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nymag.com/news/sports/games/62368/|first=Will|last=Leitch|title=No Holding Back This Holliday Season|date=2009-11-28|work=NYmag.com|publisher=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|access-date=2010-03-29|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423120054/https://nymag.com/news/sports/games/62368/}}</ref>，其中[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]的{{le|邁克·瓦卡羅|Mike Vaccaro}}更是將其和[[伊諾斯·史勞特|伊諾斯·史勞特]]於{{wsy|1946}}的那次{{le|史勞特的狂奔|Slaughter's Mad Dash|「狂奔」}}相提並論<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/sports/yankees/this_fall_this_team_is_rod_DB5iolugqEFjDhEsdir6bJ/1|title=This fall, this team, is A-Rod's|last=Vaccaro|first=Mike|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|date=2009-11-02|access-date=2011-02-24|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606173012/http://www.nypost.com/p/sports/yankees/this_fall_this_team_is_rod_DB5iolugqEFjDhEsdir6bJ/1|archive-date=2011-06-06}}</ref>。部分評論家相信戴蒙成功連盜兩壘的舉動，讓李吉在該局綁手綁腳，不敢使用有著急遽下滑幅度的拿手[[滑球|滑球]]，深怕投出[[暴投|暴投]]讓戴蒙從三壘跑回得分<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/extras/extra_bases/2009/11/hes_no_idiot_af.html|title=He's no idiot after all|last=Abraham|first=Peter|work=[[Boston_Globe|Boston Globe]]|date=2009-11-02|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073007/http://www.boston.com/sports/baseball/redsox/extras/extra_bases/2009/11/hes_no_idiot_af.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/playoffs/2009-11-02-series-breakdown_N.htm|title=Series breakdown: Veteran Damon makes grand theft|last=White|first=Paul|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2009-11-02|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2011-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211214520/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/baseball/playoffs/2009-11-02-series-breakdown_N.htm}}</ref>。特薛拉後來遭觸身球保送，之後A-ROD補上二壘安打送回戴蒙得分，洋基隊再次取得領先<ref name="game4bref"/>。下一棒波沙達也擊出一壘安打送回特薛拉和A-ROD擴大洋基隊的領先，但他在試圖衝往二壘時被觸殺而結束了這個半局<ref name="game4bref"/>。[[馬里安諾·李維拉|馬里安諾·李維拉]]在九局下半登板救援，僅以八球就完成個人系列賽第二次[[救援成功|救援成功]]，助隊取得系列賽3勝1敗的領先<ref name="game4bref"/>。

