==轉播==
{{le|福斯美國職棒大聯盟|Fox Major League Baseball|福斯體育}}已在美國連續十年轉播世界大賽，並派出[[體育評述員|主播]][[喬·巴克|喬·巴克]]及{{le|球評|Color commentator}}{{le|提姆·麥卡佛|Tim McCarver}}進行播報。本次世界大賽亦在{{le|ESPN美國職棒大聯盟廣播台|Major League Baseball on ESPN Radio|ESPN}}進行廣播轉播，由{{le|強·米勒|Jon Miller}}和[[喬·摩根|喬·摩根]]負責播報。{{le|福斯體育西語頻道|Fox Deportes}}則為美國[[西語|西語]]觀眾提供世界大賽轉播<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/fox-sports-en-espanol-announces-exclusive-spanish-language-programming-for-the-2009-world-series-with-pre---postgame-analysis-by-chicago-white-sox-manager-ozzie-guillen-66403607.html|title=Fox Sports en Espanol Announces Exclusive Spanish-Language Programming For The 2009 World Series|publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|date=2009-10-28|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606062307/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/fox-sports-en-espanol-announces-exclusive-spanish-language-programming-for-the-2009-world-series-with-pre---postgame-analysis-by-chicago-white-sox-manager-ozzie-guillen-66403607.html}}</ref>。兩隊的[[旗艦台|旗艦台]]廣播都由各自地方播報員負責轉播：費城地區由{{le|WPHT}}負責費城人隊主場的英語轉播，由{{le|史考特·弗蘭澤克|Scott Franzke}}、{{le|湯姆·麥卡錫 (播報員)|Tom McCarthy (broadcaster)|湯姆·麥卡錫}}、{{le|克里斯·惠勒|Chris Wheeler}}、{{le|賴瑞·安德森|Larry Andersen}}和{{le|蓋瑞·馬修|Gary Matthews}}負責轉播，而{{le|WDAS (AM)|WDAS (AM)|WUBA}}則負責球隊的西語轉播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.philly.com/2009-11-04/sports/24987832_1_ryan-howard-hideki-matsui-johnny-damon|title=Phillies–Yankees: World Series Game 6 preview|work=[[The_Philadelphia_Inquirer|The Philadelphia Inquirer]]|date=2009-11-04|first=Marcus|last=Hayes|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002843/http://articles.philly.com/2009-11-04/sports/24987832_1_ryan-howard-hideki-matsui-johnny-damon}}</ref>。而紐約地區則由[[WCBS_(AM)|WCBS]]負責紐約隊主場的英語轉播，由{{le|約翰·斯特林 (體育播報員)|John Sterling (sportscaster)|約翰·斯特林}}和{{le|薩辛·瓦德曼|Suzyn Waldman}}負責轉播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.recordonline.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20091028/SPORTS/910280350/-1/rss02|title=World Series: How to follow the Yankees on TV, radio|work={{le|Times Herald-Record}}|date=2009-10-28|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2011-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110617052708/http://www.recordonline.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20091028%2FSPORTS%2F910280350%2F-1%2Frss02}}</ref>。本次轉播讓瓦德曼成為第一位在廣播中轉播世界大賽的女播報員<ref>{{cite web | url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4604021&campaign=rss&source=MLBHeadlines | title=Yankees honor Waldman before Game 1 | author=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]] | publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures | date=2009-10-28 | access-date=2011-02-24 | archive-date=2012-11-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104022701/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/news/story?id=4604021&campaign=rss&source=MLBHeadlines }}</ref>。另外，{{le|XM衛星廣播|XM Satellite Radio}}也提供各戰多個訊號源給其訂閱者觀看<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://investor.sirius.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=414472|title=SIRIUS XM Radio Announces Extensive MLB Postseason Coverage|publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]] via xmradio.com|date=2009-10-07|access-date=2011-02-24|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720065449/http://investor.sirius.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=414472|archive-date=2011-07-20}}</ref>。

===收視率===
2009年世界大賽的收視率極佳，第一戰就有1950萬名觀眾數，2000年後收視率僅次於[[2004年世界大賽|2004年世界大賽]]的開幕戰，更是比{{wsy|2008}}的開幕戰高出29%<ref name="game1ratingsa">{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091030&content_id=7580380&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy&partnerId=rss_nyy |title=Buzz growing as Series has classic feel |work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]] |last=Newman |first=Mark |date=2009-10-30 |access-date=2009-11-02 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103225641/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091030&content_id=7580380&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy&partnerId=rss_nyy }}</ref><ref name="game1tratings">{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/10/29/world-series-game-1-up-29-over-2008-second-highest-game-1-of-decade/32013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012142033/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2009/10/29/world-series-game-1-up-29-over-2008-second-highest-game-1-of-decade/32013/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2012-10-12 |title=World Series Game 1 up 29% over 2008; Second highest game 1 of decade|work=Fox Sports|publisher=TV By the Numbers |date=2009-10-29|access-date=2010-01-06}}</ref>。另外，第四戰也以2280萬觀眾數成為系列賽最多人觀看的一場，同時成為自2004年以來最多人觀看的第四戰，以及成為自2001年以來「非決戰第四場」最多人觀看的一年<ref name="game4tratings"/>。2009年世界大賽平均每場獲得11.7的收視率，係自2004年世界大賽以來最高，也是自2007年至今唯二世界大賽平均每場收視率上十位數之一，另外一年即[[2016年世界大賽|2016年世界大賽]]<ref group="註">詳細可參見{{le|世界大賽電視收視率|World Series television ratings}}</ref><ref name="WSRating">{{cite web|author=Mitch Metcalf|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/skedball-world-series-ratings-through-game-7-2.html|title=World Series Ratings through Game 7|website=Showbuzz Daily|date=November 3, 2016|access-date=November 3, 2016|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104141145/http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/skedball-world-series-ratings-through-game-7-2.html}}</ref>。

