irst=Mark|last=Newman|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-10-29|access-date=2010-01-12| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100119120504/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091029&content_id=7573566&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2010-01-19| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2009/magazine/specials/sportsman/2009/11/25/derek.jeter/index.html |title=Sports Illustrated names Derek Jeter Sportsman of the Year |work=SI.com |publisher=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]] |date=2009-11-30 |access-date=2010-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100104232602/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2009/magazine/specials/sportsman/2009/11/25/derek.jeter/index.html |archive-date=2010-01-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[松井秀喜|松井秀喜]]因其表現拿下了[[世界大賽最有價值球員獎|世界大賽最有價值球員獎]]，成為首位贏得此殊榮的日籍球員與全職[[指定打擊|指定打擊]]<ref name="statsui"/><ref>{{cite news| author = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | title = Matsui Becomes 1st Japanese-Born World Series MVP | work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date =2009-11-05 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2009/11/05/sports/AP-BBO-World-Series-MVP.html | access-date =2009-11-05}}</ref>。松井秀喜也是繼前[[明尼蘇達雙城隊|明尼蘇達雙城隊]]球員{{le|丹·格拉登|Dan Gladden}}<ref group="註">他曾代表[[讀賣巨人隊|讀賣巨人隊]]於{{le|1994年日本大賽|1994 Japan Series}}出賽，並與同為球隊一員的松井秀喜一同奪冠</ref>後，第二名於北美和日本都贏得過職棒冠軍的球員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thescore.com/mlb/news/1819933|title=The year that Japanese baseball – and its stars – stepped into the American spotlight|first=Nick|last=Faris|work=The Score|access-date=2021-01-17}}</ref>。本次世界大賽有不少相關事物被送往[[美國國家棒球名人堂暨博物館|美國國家棒球名人堂暨博物館]]，其中包括當年基特和松井秀喜所使用的球棒；李維拉、李和派提特的球帽；以及[[強尼·戴蒙|強尼·戴蒙]]的{{le|防滑鞋|Cleat (shoe)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7621018&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Cooperstown to capture Series relics|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|access-date=2010-03-16|date=2009-11-05|first=Tim|last=Britton|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103104100/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7621018&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb}}</ref>。

