洋基隊在贏下本次世界大賽後，隊史冠軍數來到了27座<ref name="APYankswin"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/05/sports/baseball/05series.html?_r=1&ref=global|title=Back on Top, Yankees Add a 27th Title|last=Kepner|first=Tyler|date=2009-11-05|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2009-11-05|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075501/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/05/sports/baseball/05series.html?_r=1&ref=global}}</ref>，遠超其他任何北美職業運動隊伍的紀錄。這座冠軍是洋基隊啟用[[洋基體育場|新球場]]的第一年就拿下，而他們在前一座[[洋基體育場_(1923年)|老洋基體育場]]也同樣是啟用的第一年就贏得[[1923年世界大賽|當年世界大賽]]的冠軍<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news?slug=ge-yankeesclinch110409|title=Yankees christen new stadium with a title|date=2009-11-04|first=Gordon|last=Edes|publisher=Yahoo! Sports|access-date=2011-02-24|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025151138/http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news?slug=ge-yankeesclinch110409}}</ref>。有些體育寫手將本座冠軍視作[[艾力士·羅德里奎茲|艾力士·羅德里奎茲]]的個人成功，因為他拿下了個人首座世界大賽冠軍，並在季後賽表現優異，擺脫了先前被稱為「窒息者和輸家（choker and a loser）」的惡名<ref name="bryantarod">{{cite web|title=Postseason had many defining moments |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=bryant_howard&id=4628594 |work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]] |publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures |first=Howard |last=Bryant |date=2009-11-06 |access-date=2009-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091118154227/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=bryant_howard&id=4628594 |archive-date=2009-11-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="caplearod">{{cite web|title=A-Rod finally wins that elusive title|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=caple_jim&id=4624978|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|first=Jim|last=Caple|date=2009-11-04|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|access-date=2009-12-28|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104075705/http://sports.espn.go.com/mlb/playoffs/2009/columns/story?columnist=caple_jim&id=4624978}}</ref><ref name="DiComoARod">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091105&content_id=7624852&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Humbled A-Rod soaks in first championship|first=Anthony|last=DiComo|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-05|access-date=2009-12-28| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100119132950/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091105&content_id=7624852&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2010-01-19| dead-url= no}}</ref>。A-ROD在此次世界大賽前已出賽2,166場正規季賽，但從未參加過世界大賽，是當時活躍球員中除[[小肯·葛瑞菲|小肯·葛瑞菲]]外最多的<ref name="bryantarod"/><ref name="DiComoARod"/>。

洋基隊奪冠的關鍵歸功於多個不同的來源<ref name="spreadclues">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7621016&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Start spreadin' the clues: Why Yanks won|first=Jenifer|last=Langosch|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-05|access-date=2009-01-06|archive-date=2014-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814004502/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7621016&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb}}</ref>：許多球員都因優秀表現而深受好評，包括世界大賽MVP[[松井秀喜|松井秀喜]]<ref name="statsui"/>；休賽季期間簽下的[[馬克·特薛拉|馬克·特薛拉]]、[[C·C·沙巴西亞|C·C·沙巴西亞]]、[[A·J·柏奈特|A·J·柏奈特]]<ref name="huffingtonafter">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/11/04/yankees-win-world-series_n_346445.html|title=Yankees Win World Series: New York Beats Phillies For Record 27th Championship|first=Mike|last=Fitzpatrick|work=The Huffington Post|date=2009-11-04|access-date=2009-01-06|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235812/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/11/04/yankees-win-world-series_n_346445.html}}</ref>；以及被稱為洋基隊{{le|核心四人|Core Four}}的[[德瑞克·基特|德瑞克·基特]]、[[馬里安諾·李維拉|馬里安諾·李維拉]]、[[安迪·派提特|安迪·派提特]]以及[[荷黑·波沙達|荷黑·波沙達]]，他們全曾於1990年代為洋基隊打下當時的王朝霸業<ref name="sixfivefour">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7620796&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Six games, five rings, four Yankees|first=Bryan|last=Hoch|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-05|access-date=2009-01-06|archive-date=2014-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814003130/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7620796&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb}}</ref><ref name="timescore">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/26/sports/26anderson.html|title=Sports of the Times; From Yanks' Core To Pacquiao, Plenty of Cheers|first=Dave|last=Anderson|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2009-11-29|access-date=2009-01-06|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075502/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/11/26/sports/26anderson.html}}</ref><ref name="pettitefive">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7620800&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Pettitte relishes fifth championship ring|first=Thomas|last=Boorstein|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-05|access-date=2010-01-06| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100119133049/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7620800&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2010-01-19| dead-url= no}}</ref>。總教練[[喬·吉拉迪|喬·吉拉迪]]出色的表現也歸於他的帶隊管理<ref name="girardi">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091105&content_id=7625028&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Girardi leads Yankees to ultimate goal|first=Thomas|last=Boorstein|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-05|access-date=2010-01-06| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100119132936/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091105&content_id=7625028&vkey=ps2009news&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2010-01-19| dead-url= no}}</ref>，特別是他決定以三先發作為洋基隊季後賽的{{le|先發輪值|starting rotation}}模式<ref name="3manpt2">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7621188&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy|title=In the end, Girardi's pitching plan pays off|first=Jennifer|last=Langosch|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2009-11-05|access-date=2010-01-06| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100119085954/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091104&content_id=7621188&vkey=news_nyy&fext=.jsp&c_id=nyy| archive-date=2010-01-19| dead-url= no}}</ref>。洋基隊是自{{wsy|1998}}的{{le|1998年聖地牙哥教士隊球季|1998 San Diego Padres season|聖地牙哥教士隊}}以來，首支在世界大賽中僅用三先發的球隊<ref name="batsblog"/>。

