date=2010-01-08|access-date=2010-01-11|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725193507/http://www.presidencia.gob.do/app/article.aspx?id=11838|archive-date=2011-07-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100108&content_id=7892702&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|title=Yanks, trophy tour Dominican Republic|first=Bryan|last=Hoch|work=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball|Major League Baseball]]|date=2010-01-07|access-date=2010-01-11| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100115113930/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20100108&content_id=7892702&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb| archive-date=2010-01-15| dead-url= no}}</ref>。洋基隊2009年冠軍隊成員多數在隔年開幕日，就領到屬於他們的{{le|冠軍戒|Championship ring}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/2010-04-13/sports/27061526_1_rings-balfour-college-style|title=New York Yankees set for 2010 Opening Day with World Series rings in hand|access-date=2011-02-27|last=Bondy|first=Filip|work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|date=2010-04-13|archive-date=2012-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120801151751/http://articles.nydailynews.com/2010-04-13/sports/27061526_1_rings-balfour-college-style}}</ref>，而於2010年轉到天使隊的松井秀喜，則是於天使隊當年首次作客布朗克斯參加洋基隊主場開幕戰時，由洋基隊呈給他戒指<ref>{{cite news|title=Jeter plays ring prank on Matsui|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/los-angeles/mlb/news/story?id=5083131|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=2010-04-13|access-date=2011-02-27|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117021239/http://sports.espn.go.com/los-angeles/mlb/news/story?id=5083131}}</ref>。此外他們也於2010年4月前往[[白宮|白宮]]拜會時任美國總統[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]，並送給總統簽名球衣<ref>{{cite news|title=Obama hosts Yankees at White House|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/news/story?id=5137815|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=2010-04-26|access-date=2011-02-27|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117030740/http://sports.espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/news/story?id=5137815}}</ref>。

隔季洋基隊以{{le|美國職棒大聯盟外卡|Major League Baseball wild card|外卡}}身分重返季後賽，但他們在[[2010年美國聯盟冠軍賽|2010年美聯冠軍賽]]上敗給[[德州遊騎兵隊|德州遊騎兵隊]]，其中還包括被前費城人隊王牌[[克里夫·李|克里夫·李]]以8比0完封，這場之後克里夫·李已取得季後賽七連勝，其中三勝就是從洋基隊手中取得。洋基隊曾於2010年賽季試圖從[[西雅圖水手隊|西雅圖水手隊]]交易來克里夫·李，但最終以交易失敗告終<ref>{{Cite web|last=Leonardi|first=Stephen|date=2020-07-10|title=On this day in Yankees history: The Cliff Lee trade that never was|url=http://bronxpinstripes.com/yankees-history/on-this-day-in-yankees-history-the-cliff-lee-trade-that-never-was/|access-date=2020-12-07|website=Bronx Pinstripes {{!}} BronxPinstripes.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075510/http://bronxpinstripes.com/yankees-history/on-this-day-in-yankees-history-the-cliff-lee-trade-that-never-was/}}</ref>。後來洋基隊曾於[[2012年美國聯盟冠軍賽|2012年]]、[[2017年美國聯盟冠軍賽|2017年]]及[[2019年美國聯盟冠軍賽|2019年]]再次打入[[美聯冠軍賽|美聯冠軍賽]]，但均鎩羽而歸，未能重演打入世界大賽的光景<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=301022113&print=1|title=Rangers headed to World Series for first time|date=2010-10-22|first=Stephen|last=Hawkins|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Yahoo! Sports|access-date=2011-02-19|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305144242/https://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/recap?gid=301022113&print=1}}</ref>。

===費城人隊===
洋基隊在第四戰勝出取得三勝一敗的領先後，[[費城詢問報|費城詢問報]]不慎將[[美斯百貨|美斯百貨]]恭賀費城人隊世界大賽奪冠的四分之三頁廣告登出，上頭還附有費城人隊冠軍[[T恤|T恤]]的圖樣，詢問報隨後也為此作出道歉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=4616770&type=story|title=Newspaper apologizes for incorrect ad|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|agency=Associated Press|date=2009-11-02|access-date=2010-03-30|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111152936/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=4616770&type=story}}</ref>。

[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]的專欄作家李·詹金斯（Lee Jenkins）將費城人隊敗陣的原因歸因於投手陣容的深度，並指出洋基隊在系列賽中共三名不同的先發投手奪勝，而費城人隊只有[[克里夫·李|克里夫·李]]拿過勝投。費城人隊2008年季後賽時的強投們（包括先發投手[[科爾·漢梅爾斯|科爾·漢梅爾斯]]及終結者[[布萊德·李吉|布萊德·李吉]]），在本屆世界大賽各自唯一出賽時都表現的相當掙扎。而曾於國聯冠軍賽表現極佳的費城人隊牛棚，也在世界大賽中接連失手，光是在{{frac|11|2|3}}局的投球中，就失掉七分自責分，防禦率高達5.40。<ref name="phildepth">{{cite news|url=http://si.printthis.clickability.com/pt/cpt?action=cpt&title=Lack+of+starting+pitching+depth+doomed+Philadelphia+Phillies+-+Lee+Jenkins+-+SI.com&expire=&urlID=414147432&fb=Y&url=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsillustrated.cnn.com%2F2009%2Fwriters%2Flee_jenkins%2F11%2F05%2Fpedro.martinez%2Findex.html&partnerID=2356|title=Lack of pitching depth cost Phillies|last=Jenkins|first=Lee|date=2009-11-05|work=SI.com|publisher=[[Sports_Illustrated|Sports Illustrated]]|access-date=2010-01-21|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075501/http://si.printthis.clickability.com/pt/cpt?action=cpt&title=Lack+of+starting+pitching+depth+doomed+Philadelphia+Phillies+-+Lee+Jenkins+-+SI.com&expire=&urlID=414147432&fb=Y&url=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsillustrated.cnn.com%2F2009%2Fwriters%2Flee_jenkins%2F11%2F05%2Fpedro.martinez%2Findex.html&partnerID=2356}}</ref>ESPN的小豪爾赫·阿蘭古爾（Jorge Arangure Jr.）則將費城人隊的敗北部分原因歸咎於缺乏打擊的攻勢，並指出全隊在世界大賽中的打擊率僅2成27。只有整個系列賽打出五發全壘打的[[蔡斯·阿特利|蔡斯·阿特利]]表現優異，而且他還貢獻費城人隊所有90個壘打數中的22個，與此相較，[[謝恩·維克托里諾|謝恩·維克托里諾]]及[[吉米·羅林斯|吉米·羅林斯]]的打擊表現都相當掙扎，而國聯冠軍賽MVP[[萊恩·霍華德|萊恩·霍華德]]更是在世界大賽中苦吞13次三振。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=4624839&type=story|title=Five reasons the Phillies didn't repeat|last=Arangure|first=Jorge Jr.|work=[[ESPN.com|ESPN.com]]|publisher=ESPN Internet Ventures|date=2009-11-04|access-date=2010-03-31|archive-date=2013-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111152939/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/print?id=4624839&type=story}}</ref>

{{mlby|2010}}賽季開打前，費城人隊重組投手群以提升投手戰力：首先在同一個四方2009年季後賽上的王牌投手克里夫·李交易走<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091216&content_id=7817826&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-12-19 |archive-date=2013-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131126222732/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091216&content_id=7817826&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/mariners/2010522667_mari17.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629070604/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/mariners/2010522667_mari17.html |archivedate=2011-06-29 }}</ref>，並交易來[[多倫多藍鳥隊|多倫多藍鳥隊]]王牌投手[[羅伊·哈勒戴|羅伊·哈勒戴]]<ref name="mlb20091216">{{cite web |url=http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20091216&content_id=7818010&vkey=pr_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi |title=Phillies acquire Halladay |date=2009-12-16 |publisher=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]] |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-date=2017-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108034856/http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20091216&content_id=7818010&vkey=pr_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091215&content_id=7814772&vkey=news_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi|title=Seven prospects involved in blockbuster|date=2009-12-16|author=Mayo, Jonathan and Winston, Lisa|publisher=[[MLB.com|MLB.com]]|accessdate=2009-12-17|archive-date=2014-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326175100/http://philadelphia.phillies.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20091215&content_id=7814772&vkey=news_phi&fext=.jsp&c_id=phi|dead-url=no}}</ref>。費城人隊後來於2010年以全聯盟最佳戰績重返季後賽，但於[[2010年國家聯盟冠軍賽|國聯冠軍賽]]中敗給當年冠軍{{le|2010年舊金山巨人隊球季|2010 San Francisco Giants season|舊金山巨人隊}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Giants Punch Out Phillies, Looking|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/24/sports/baseball/24nlcs.html?_r=1&pagewanted=print|date=2010-10-24|first=David|last=Waldstein|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2011-01-23|page=SP1|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423121515/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/24/sports/baseball/24nlcs.html?_r=1&pagewanted=print}}</ref>。克里夫李於2011年成為自由球員後，重新與費城人隊簽約加盟，連同2010年交易大限前來到費城人隊的[[洛伊·奧斯華|洛伊·奧斯華]]，加上已在陣中科爾·漢梅爾斯和羅伊·哈勒戴，並稱費城人隊的「'''四大王牌'''（The Four Aces）」<ref>{{Cite news|last=Jordan|first=Pat|date=2011-03-31|title=The Phillies' Four Aces (Published 2011)|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/03/magazine/mag-03Phillies-t.html|access-date=2020-12-21|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303003648/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/03/magazine/mag-03Phillies-t.html}}</ref>。 如此豪華的陣容加上更有經驗的打線，讓費城人隊再度成為世界大賽冠軍的大熱門，但他們卻在當年[[2011年國家聯盟分區賽|國聯分區賽]]五戰敗給後來的冠軍{{le|2011年聖路易紅雀隊球季|2011 St. Louis Cardinals season|聖路易紅雀隊}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/25557064//|title=Cardinals, Phillies make history with 1-0 Game 5|last=Casella|first=Paul|website=MLB.com|date=2011-10-08|access-date=2021-04-21|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220145312/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/25557064/}}</ref>，結束了失望的一季，且自該年後費城人隊更是在季後賽裡一勝難求<ref>{{cite web |last1=Lagowski |first1=Kevin |title=Philadelphia Phillies: 2007-2011 run of dominance was disappointing |url=https://section215.com/2020/03/29/philadelphia-phillies-2007-2011-disappointing/ |website=FanSide |access-date=2020-05-03 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429135343/https://section215.com/2020/03/29/philadelphia-phillies-2007-2011-disappointing/ }}</ref>。

===大衛·帕特森門票醜聞===
時任[[紐約州州長|紐約州州長]][[大衛·帕特森_(政治人物)|大衛·帕特森]]也是第一戰的觀眾之一，其所屬政黨收到五張本壘板後方的門票。2010年3月3日，紐約公共誠信委員會（the New York Commission on Public Integrity）發現帕特森違反了公職人員送禮的相關{{le|州法律|State law (United States)}}，而且他還向委員會[[偽證罪|撒謊]]說他打算支付門票費<ref name="WSJSaul">{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748703862704575099663280532160?mod=WSJ_hpp_MIDDLENexttoWhatsNewsThird|title=Paterson Faulted For Ethics Slip|last=Saul|first=Michael Howard|date=2010-03-04|work=The Wall Street Journal|access-date=2010-03-04|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423120055/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748703862704575099663280532160?mod=WSJ_hpp_MIDDLENexttoWhatsNewsThird}}</ref>。委員會後來進一步發現，帕特森利用職權向洋基隊索要五張免費門票<ref group="註">每張價值達425美元</ref><ref name="NYTPeters">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/04/nyregion/04paterson.html?_r=1&pagewanted=print|title=Paterson's Ethics Breach Is Turned Over to Prosecutors|last1=Confessore|first1=Nicholas|last2=Peters|first2=Jeremy W.|date=2010-03-03|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2010-03-04|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421075459/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/04/nyregion/04paterson.html?_r=1&pagewanted=print}}</ref>，而且實情與證詞完全不同，他不僅從未想為這些門票付錢，以他之名所發的支票也是在案子開始調查後才寫出<ref name="WSJSaul" /><ref name="NYTPeters" />。為此，委員會對帕特森判處6萬2125美元的罰款<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/12/20/gov-paterson-fined-62125-for-taking-world-series-tickets/|title=Governor Paterson Fined Over World Series Tickets|last=Halbfinger|first=David|date=2010-12-20|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=2011-02-02| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110112093921/http://cityroom.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/12/20/gov-paterson-fined-62125-for-taking-world-series-tickets/| archive-date=2011-01-12| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

